title: Ravens revitalized after 23-20 overtime win against Steelers
text:
> Pennsylvania Ravens revitalized after 23-20 overtime win against Steelers Baltimore Ravens kicker Justin Tucker (9) celebrates as he walks to the locker room after kicking a game-winning field goal in overtime to beat the Pittsburgh Steelers 23-20 in an NFL football game in Pittsburgh, Thursday, Oct. 1, 2015. (AP Photo/Gene Puskar) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
